## Third-Party Licenses

### KST32B Font

The font rendering is based on KST32B vector font data.

```
"Kanji"+ASCII+ StrokeTable: 30x32 VectorFont by Saka.N,saka

FREE-WARE (free to copy, change...) 1992 2004 Saka.N

E-Mail: Saka.N.06@b3.mnx.ne.jp
http://www.vector.co.jp/soft/data/writing/se119277.html
```

### OpenJTalk / hts_engine_API

Voice synthesis audio files were generated using OpenJTalk and hts_engine_API.

